message: He's not wrong. This album doesn't have anything black metal in it and no Venom albums have had anything to do with black metal. Venom only came up with the name for it. They have nothing to do with black metal, they're simply just traditional NWOBHM and no different than Motorhead or Judas Priest. If you call Venom a black metal band, that's like calling Judas Priest thrash metal.
This album has nothing to do with the black metal genre.
/* June 2023 */ Reply
